		"description": "There are a number of places that constants are injected into the mobile web's index.html template and various JavaScript files where these constants are not properly escaped. If a project name has a < or > in it, it will cause invalid HTML markup.  Or if the project description has an unescaped quote, it will break the JavaScript.\r\n\r\nIntegrate the mako template engine into the build process and escape the variable insertions using the correct mako filters.\r\n\r\nRefer to the mako filtering documentation for more information: http://www.makotemplates.org/docs/documentation.html#filtering.",
